title: Smurf Leveling Up
body: Hey guys, so I just moved from California to Sydney and am wanting to level a new account here. I am currently level 11 and my other account peaked at Plat 1. Looking for someone who has a smurf to level with! Add me in game or reply here. TheWarLegend

replies.body: I'll help you get to lvl 30 if you like.

Hey, I'm not exactly your level when it comes to ranked, (Bronze 5 after S6 Promos) but I do have a smurf of around that level. Tell me if you want to play together, though I may not be at your ranked level. Thanks!
Sure hop on and add me!
Sounds great! Ill add you real soon :)
